# Learned lessons while installing / using arch

## Hints, Problems & Solutions

### GPU
- Flickering
- Bugs while taking screenshots
- Bugs while sharing the screen
=> Solution: The package "xf86-video-intel" is bugged 

### Locales
In order to use mixed locales, it's required to generate multiple locales within the file /etc/locale.gen => uncomment all required locales and run locale-gen afterwards.
